---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Vermont Property Tax Appeal Resources | Blog | VermontTaxAppeal.com"
  description="Vermont property tax grievance guides, reappraisal updates, and tax appeal resources. Learn about Grand List overassessments, deadlines, and commercial property tax strategies."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative py-28 px-6 overflow-hidden" style="background: #060a0f;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[350px] opacity-8"
           style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse, #f97316 0%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.08] mb-6">
        Vermont Property Tax<br />
        <span style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f97316, #fb923c); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">Resources & Guides</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Property tax overassessments, reappraisal cycles, deadline strategies, and real stories from Vermont property owners who reduced their taxes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BLOG POSTS -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6" style="background: #04080f;">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-12">Latest Articles</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8">

        <!-- Post 1 -->
        <article style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" class="hover:border-orange-500/30">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-3">Vermont Commercial Property Overassessment: How Town Listers Make Mistakes</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Mass appraisal models don't know about your vacant lease space, deferred maintenance, or below-market rent lock-in. We show you how to document what the Grand List missed.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
                <span>9 min read</span>
                <span>•</span>
                <span>Commercial · Chittenden County</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 font-semibold mt-4 transition-colors">
                Read Article
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Post 2 -->
        <article style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" class="hover:border-orange-500/30">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-3">Vermont Statewide Reappraisal Years: When Your Property Value Explodes (and What to Do)</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Towns like Barre, St. Johnsbury, and others face mandatory reappraisals when common level of appraisal falls below 80%. What that means for your tax bill and your grievance window.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
                <span>8 min read</span>
                <span>•</span>
                <span>Reappraisal · All Counties</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 font-semibold mt-4 transition-colors">
                Read Article
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Post 3 -->
        <article style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" class="hover:border-orange-500/30">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-3">DIY vs. Tax Appeal Consultant: When It's Worth Hiring Someone</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                You can file a grievance yourself. But a poorly documented grievance dies at the lister stage. Learn what separates winning cases from the ones that get dismissed.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
                <span>7 min read</span>
                <span>•</span>
                <span>Strategy · All Property Types</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 font-semibold mt-4 transition-colors">
                Read Article
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Post 4 -->
        <article style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" class="hover:border-orange-500/30">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-3">Vermont Property Tax Grievance Deadlines: The 30-Day Window That Changes Everything</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Miss the 30-day window under 32 V.S.A. § 4404 and you lose your right to grieve for another year. Here's how to never miss it again.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
                <span>6 min read</span>
                <span>•</span>
                <span>Deadlines · All Counties</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 font-semibold mt-4 transition-colors">
                Read Article
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Post 5 -->
        <article style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; transition: all 0.3s ease;" class="hover:border-orange-500/30">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-white mb-3">Ski Resort & Tourism Property in Vermont: Tax Assessment Strategies for Hospitality Properties</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                Lodges, ski-in rentals, and resort properties face unique appraisal challenges. Here's how seasonality, occupancy rates, and deed restrictions affect your Grand List value.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
                <span>10 min read</span>
                <span>•</span>
                <span>Hospitality · Lamoille County</span>
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-300 font-semibold mt-4 transition-colors">
                Read Article
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6" style="background: #060a0f;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249,115,22,0.08) 0%, rgba(234,88,12,0.04) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.18); border-radius: 20px;" class="p-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white mb-4">Ready to Lower Your Vermont Property Tax?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg mb-8">Send us your property details and we'll tell you straight — is there a case worth filing, and what does the savings look like?</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-10 py-4 text-base btn-orange font-semibold">
          Get Free Grievance Review
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
